Subject: [PATCH 4.19 08/32] ASoC: rsnd: Fix HDMI channel mapping for multi-SSI mode
Date:   Fri,  8 May 2020 14:35:21 +0200
Message-Id: <20200508123035.905556314@linuxfoundation.org>
